00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:26,080
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

345
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:28,720
<font color="#ffffff">Ma'am, please keep her there.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

346
00:19:28,800 --> 00:19:30,680
<font color="#ffffff">Just this one day.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

347
00:19:42,560 --> 00:19:44,280
<font color="#ffffff">-Kang?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-What?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

348
00:19:45,080 --> 00:19:46,200
<font color="#ffffff">What is it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

349
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:50,000
<font color="#ffffff">A colleague. I'll be right back.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

350
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:54,760
<font color="#ffffff">Kang.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

351
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:57,920
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, hey! Ms. Dao, what a coincidence.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

352
00:19:58,000 --> 00:20:00,000
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you here?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

353
00:20:00,080 --> 00:20:01,320
<font color="#ffffff">What about the set?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

354
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:05,000
<font color="#ffffff">Wait. Are you kidding me?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I'm on the set right now.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

355
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:07,440
<font color="#ffffff">The set is right across the street.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

356
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,360
<font color="#ffffff">What?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

357
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:11,720
<font color="#ffffff">Well, Patty's set.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

358
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:14,480
<font color="#ffffff">Patty asked for some snacks,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">so I'm buying some for her.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

359
00:20:14,560 --> 00:20:15,920
<font color="#ffffff">No.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

360
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,360
<font color="#ffffff">I mean,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

361
00:20:17,440 --> 00:20:19,400
<font color="#ffffff">why are you on Patty's set?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

362
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:21,520
<font color="#ffffff">Weren't you supposed to be at Petch's?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

363
00:20:21,600 --> 00:20:24,960
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, didn't Mr. Ake tell you yet?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

364
00:20:25,040 --> 00:20:26,000
<font color="#ffffff">Tell me what?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

365
00:20:26,080 --> 00:20:28,160
<font color="#ffffff">Mr. Ake wanted me to take care of her.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

366
00:20:28,240 --> 00:20:30,880
<font color="#ffffff">He will take care of Petch's instead.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

367
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:35,000
<font color="#ffffff">Why would he do that?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

368
00:20:35,080 --> 00:20:38,360
<font color="#ffffff">I have absolutely no idea.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not lying to you.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

369
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:41,480
<font color="#ffffff">He even said he would talk to you himself.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

370
00:20:42,280 --> 00:20:43,120
<font color="#ffffff">Okay.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

371
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:45,680
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you for telling me the truth.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

372
00:20:46,600 --> 00:20:48,960
<font color="#ffffff">Dao, invite your friend to sit with us.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

373
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:50,960
<font color="#ffffff">It's okay.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

374
00:20:51,040 --> 00:20:52,440
<font color="#ffffff">I think I have to leave now.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

375
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:55,480
<font color="#ffffff">Please tell Mom I have an urgent matter.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

376
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:02,280
<font color="#ffffff">-I'll take my leave too. Goodbye!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Okay.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

377
00:21:04,280 --> 00:21:06,160
<font color="#ffffff">Ms. Dao. Wait!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

378
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,200
<font color="#ffffff">Wait a second.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

379
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:11,080
<font color="#ffffff">Mr. Ake shouldn't have lied</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to you like this.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

380
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:14,320
<font color="#ffffff">That set must be a total mess right now.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

381
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:16,760
<font color="#ffffff">Please let me help you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

382
00:21:16,840 --> 00:21:17,760
<font color="#ffffff">It's fine.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

383
00:21:17,840 --> 00:21:19,880
<font color="#ffffff">Since you're already here,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

384
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:21,520
<font color="#ffffff">just stay and look after Patty.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

385
00:21:21,600 --> 00:21:24,000
<font color="#ffffff">I'll handle Petch's set myself.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

386
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:32,520
<font color="#ffffff">Please, heavens,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I hope nothing bad happens to that set.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

387
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:34,400
<font color="#ffffff">Bless them.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

388
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:39,760
<font color="#ffffff">It's okay, Petch. No worries.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

389
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:42,000
<font color="#ffffff">Stay focused. You can do it. Okay, ready!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

390
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:48,440
<font color="#ffffff">Walk forward.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

391
00:21:48,520 --> 00:21:49,840
<font color="#ffffff">Slowly.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

392
00:21:49,920 --> 00:21:51,000
<font color="#ffffff">Nice.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

393
00:21:51,080 --> 00:21:53,520
<font color="#ffffff">To the marked spot. Yes.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

394
00:21:54,120 --> 00:21:55,600
<font color="#ffffff">Keep looking up.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

395
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:58,120
<font color="#ffffff">Feel that she's out of reach.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

396
00:21:58,200 --> 00:21:59,240
<font color="#ffffff">Just like that!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

397
00:21:59,320 --> 00:22:01,280
<font color="#ffffff">Look high up.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

398
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:03,280
<font color="#ffffff">Yes, like that.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

399
00:22:03,360 --> 00:22:06,600
<font color="#ffffff">You try to reach for her, but you can't.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

400
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:09,240
<font color="#ffffff">She's way above you. Yes.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

401
00:22:23,800 --> 00:22:26,600
<font color="#ffffff">Cut! Wow, Petch, amazing!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

402
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:27,720
<font color="#ffffff">Did we get it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

403
00:22:27,800 --> 00:22:30,600
<font color="#ffffff">Of course, we did!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

404
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:32,040
<font color="#ffffff">That's a one-take pass!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

405
00:22:32,120 --> 00:22:35,240
<font color="#ffffff">Give this guy an Oscar!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

406
00:22:35,320 --> 00:22:38,920
<font color="#ffffff">-You're exaggerating.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Seriously, though.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

407
00:22:39,520 --> 00:22:41,160
<font color="#ffffff">With that look in your eyes,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

408
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:44,120
<font color="#ffffff">did some rich girl break your heart? Huh?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

409
00:22:45,240 --> 00:22:48,720
<font color="#ffffff">What? Come on!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

410
00:22:48,800 --> 00:22:50,800
<font color="#ffffff">Spill it!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

411
00:22:51,480 --> 00:22:53,240
<font color="#ffffff">-Time is limited.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Hey!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

412
00:22:53,320 --> 00:22:54,280
<font color="#ffffff">Let's move on.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

413
00:22:54,360 --> 00:22:57,280
<font color="#ffffff">Wow, you're really good</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">at changing the subject.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

414
00:22:57,360 --> 00:22:58,840
<font color="#ffffff">So incredible.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

415
00:22:58,920 --> 00:23:00,000
<font color="#ffffff">All right, everyone…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

416
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:04,640
<font color="#ffffff">Will Petch drive through the explosion</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">from this side?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

417
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:06,320
<font color="#ffffff">Yes, great.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

418
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:08,400
<font color="#ffffff">-Get the special effects ready.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-All right.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

419
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:11,640
<font color="#ffffff">Where's the prop team?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Let me see the car. Hey, prop team!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

420
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:13,160
<font color="#ffffff">Bring the car over!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

421
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:14,320
<font color="#ffffff">Is it ready?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

422
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:16,480
<font color="#ffffff">Here it is, sir.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

423
00:23:18,360 --> 00:23:19,440
<font color="#ffffff">Hey, wait!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

424
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:21,400
<font color="#ffffff">A motorbike?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

425
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:22,720
<font color="#ffffff">Are you out of your mind?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

426
00:23:22,800 --> 00:23:23,640
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

427
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:24,840
<font color="#ffffff">It's Mr. Ake's order.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

428
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,960
<font color="#ffffff">Are you insane?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

429
00:23:27,040 --> 00:23:28,600
<font color="#ffffff">I ordered a car!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

430
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:29,520
<font color="#ffffff">Not a motorbike!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

431
00:23:30,120 --> 00:23:33,520
<font color="#ffffff">Darn it! I'm going crazy!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I'm going to lose my mind!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

432
00:23:34,440 --> 00:23:36,040
<font color="#ffffff">What are you complaining about?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

433
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:38,160
<font color="#ffffff">When will you start shooting?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

434
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:42,080
<font color="#ffffff">Mr. Ake, I'm glad you're here.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

435
00:23:42,160 --> 00:23:43,600
<font color="#ffffff">I ordered a car,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

436
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:45,440
<font color="#ffffff">so why change it to a motorbike?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

437
00:23:45,520 --> 00:23:46,840
<font color="#ffffff">He can use it too.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

438
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:48,640
<font color="#ffffff">And it's cheaper.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

439
00:23:48,720 --> 00:23:51,240
<font color="#ffffff">Why should we pay</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">for an expensive car rental?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

440
00:23:51,320 --> 00:23:54,080
<font color="#ffffff">But you can't change it</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">in the middle of a shoot!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

441
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:55,280
<font color="#ffffff">That's the whole budget.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

442
00:23:56,240 --> 00:23:57,520
<font color="#ffffff">Are you shooting or not?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

443
00:23:59,000 --> 00:23:59,920
<font color="#ffffff">Jeez!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

444
00:24:01,160 --> 00:24:02,200
<font color="#ffffff">I am, obviously!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

445
00:24:02,280 --> 00:24:04,440
<font color="#ffffff">You completely forced my hand here.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

446
00:24:05,320 --> 00:24:06,840
<font color="#ffffff">A motorbike is fine!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

447
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:09,040
<font color="#ffffff">Stunt double!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

448
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:11,240
<font color="#ffffff">Where is he? Get him here!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

449
00:24:11,840 --> 00:24:13,240
<font color="#ffffff">I've canceled him.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

450
00:24:14,600 --> 00:24:16,200
<font color="#ffffff">You seriously have?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

451
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,200
<font color="#ffffff">Why not?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

452
00:24:18,280 --> 00:24:19,520
<font color="#ffffff">Simply riding a motorbike</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

453
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:21,520
<font color="#ffffff">doesn't need a stuntman.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

454
00:24:21,600 --> 00:24:23,880
<font color="#ffffff">But he has to ride in explosions!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

455
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:25,440
<font color="#ffffff">Or will you ride it yourself?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

456
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:26,800
<font color="#ffffff">Don't talk back to me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

457
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:29,320
<font color="#ffffff">If you can't shoot it,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">just call off the set.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

458
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:33,080
<font color="#ffffff">Many scenes are done.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

459
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:35,240
<font color="#ffffff">Why would we call it off?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

460
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:37,760
<font color="#ffffff">Listen, Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

461
00:24:37,840 --> 00:24:39,560
<font color="#ffffff">I don't have a stuntman for you.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

462
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:41,040
<font color="#ffffff">So what?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

463
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:42,000
<font color="#ffffff">I can do it myself.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

464
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:45,280
<font color="#ffffff">It's risky. Can you really handle it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

465
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:47,320
<font color="#ffffff">If we don't do it, the work is over.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

466
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,760
<font color="#ffffff">Let's just talk about the cues.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

467
00:24:52,280 --> 00:24:54,520
<font color="#ffffff">Petch, my dear brother!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

468
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:56,120
<font color="#ffffff">You've got real guts!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

469
00:24:56,200 --> 00:25:00,680
<font color="#ffffff">You've got balls of steel,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">unlike some cowardly executives.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

470
00:25:01,880 --> 00:25:04,080
<font color="#ffffff">Incredible, my man!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

471
00:25:04,720 --> 00:25:05,880
<font color="#ffffff">Let's get to work!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

472
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:07,040
<font color="#ffffff">Hey, move it!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

473
00:25:07,120 --> 00:25:10,320
<font color="#ffffff">Everyone, come! Hey, you, stop eating!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

474
00:25:20,360 --> 00:25:22,320
<font color="#ffffff">-Okay.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Wait for Petch.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

475
00:25:22,400 --> 00:25:23,400
<font color="#ffffff">All set?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

476
00:25:25,440 --> 00:25:26,520
<font color="#ffffff">Ride from over there.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

477
00:25:26,600 --> 00:25:28,240
<font color="#ffffff">There will be six explosions,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

478
00:25:28,320 --> 00:25:31,080
<font color="#ffffff">but our crew will give you the cues.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

479
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:33,480
<font color="#ffffff">You can go stand by over there</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

480
00:25:33,560 --> 00:25:36,400
<font color="#ffffff">and just follow their signals.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

481
00:25:36,480 --> 00:25:37,400
<font color="#ffffff">Okay?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

482
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:38,880
<font color="#ffffff">Go straight this way, right?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

483
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:41,040
<font color="#ffffff">Yes, and go up the ramp.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

484
00:25:41,120 --> 00:25:42,000
<font color="#ffffff">So, Petch…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

485
00:25:44,160 --> 00:25:45,960
<font color="#ffffff">Should I go ahead</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

486
00:25:46,800 --> 00:25:48,480
<font color="#ffffff">and pick out a coffin for you?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

487
00:25:50,840 --> 00:25:52,400
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, my.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

488
00:25:52,480 --> 00:25:54,440
<font color="#ffffff">Just kidding. Don't be so serious.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

489
00:25:55,320 --> 00:25:56,680
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not afraid of dying.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

490
00:25:58,600 --> 00:26:00,000
<font color="#ffffff">Fake people</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

491
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:01,520
<font color="#ffffff">are way scarier.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

492
00:26:06,560 --> 00:26:07,560
<font color="#ffffff">Petch!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

493
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:08,520
<font color="#ffffff">Ready?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

494
00:26:09,320 --> 00:26:10,160
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

495
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:11,080
<font color="#ffffff">Great!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

496
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:14,560
<font color="#ffffff">If you're ready,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">let's shoot this. Let's go.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

497
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:16,800
<font color="#ffffff">Everyone, let's go!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

498
00:26:18,040 --> 00:26:20,400
<font color="#ffffff">Petch, this way.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

499
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,200
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

500
00:26:31,600 --> 00:26:32,920
<font color="#ffffff">Keep acting tough.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

501
00:26:33,840 --> 00:26:36,200
<font color="#ffffff">I'll watch you get blown to bits.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

502
00:26:42,840 --> 00:26:44,080
<font color="#ffffff">Which scene now?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

503
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:48,520
<font color="#ffffff">We're shooting a motorbike</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">riding through explosions.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

504
00:26:48,600 --> 00:26:50,720
<font color="#ffffff">Petch will ride it himself.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

505
00:26:50,800 --> 00:26:53,160
<font color="#ffffff">What? I thought it was a car.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

506
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:55,920
<font color="#ffffff">Where's the stuntman?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Why is he riding it himself?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

507
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:57,640
<font color="#ffffff">I have no idea either.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

508
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:59,080
<font color="#ffffff">Who changed it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

509
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:00,960
<font color="#ffffff">Mr. Akekaphol.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

510
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:10,840
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

511
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:12,640
<font color="#ffffff">Hey, Dao!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

512
00:27:13,560 --> 00:27:15,240
<font color="#ffffff">They're rolling. Don't get in.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

513
00:27:15,320 --> 00:27:16,360
<font color="#ffffff">Let go of me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

514
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:17,920
<font color="#ffffff">How could you do this, Ake?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

515
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:20,160
<font color="#ffffff">What did I do?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

516
00:27:20,240 --> 00:27:22,280
<font color="#ffffff">You said you would behave.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

517
00:27:22,360 --> 00:27:24,920
<font color="#ffffff">Then why did you make Petch</font><font color="#ffffff">
