00:48:50,000 --> 00:48:53,920
<font color="#ffffff">YOUR PARENTS WOULD BE UPSET</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">SEEING MY FACE,<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

866
00:48:54,000 --> 00:48:59,120
<font color="#ffffff">BUT I'M CONTENT</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">JUST WATCHING OVER YOU FROM RIGHT HERE.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

867
00:49:24,120 --> 00:49:24,960
<font color="#ffffff">Ake?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

868
00:49:25,840 --> 00:49:26,680
<font color="#ffffff">What is it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

869
00:49:28,520 --> 00:49:32,400
<font color="#ffffff">I just came up to escort my fiancé</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">down to the party.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

870
00:49:35,480 --> 00:49:37,240
<font color="#ffffff">You look absolutely stunning today.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

871
00:49:39,880 --> 00:49:41,800
<font color="#ffffff">Hey! Let go of me, Ake!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

872
00:49:41,880 --> 00:49:44,160
<font color="#ffffff">You're so beautiful.</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Let me hold you for a second.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

873
00:49:44,240 --> 00:49:46,040
<font color="#ffffff">-Let go!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Just a hug. Nothing else.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

874
00:49:46,120 --> 00:49:47,560
<font color="#ffffff">Ake, get off!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

875
00:49:51,040 --> 00:49:53,200
<font color="#ffffff">You said you'd be better.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

876
00:49:53,280 --> 00:49:56,760
<font color="#ffffff">We've barely started,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and you're showing your true colors now.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

877
00:49:57,360 --> 00:49:58,320
<font color="#ffffff">Dao!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

878
00:49:58,400 --> 00:50:00,320
<font color="#ffffff">We're engaged.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

879
00:50:00,400 --> 00:50:02,880
<font color="#ffffff">Can't you let me show you</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">any affection at all?<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

880
00:50:02,960 --> 00:50:04,280
<font color="#ffffff">We're just engaged,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

881
00:50:04,360 --> 00:50:05,960
<font color="#ffffff">not married!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

882
00:50:06,600 --> 00:50:09,840
<font color="#ffffff">Don't you ever lay a hand on me again!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

883
00:50:15,320 --> 00:50:16,960
<font color="#ffffff">Just you wait.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

884
00:50:17,040 --> 00:50:18,560
<font color="#ffffff">Tonight, you'll see what's coming.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

885
00:50:20,320 --> 00:50:22,720
<font color="#ffffff">You know how stubborn Dao can be.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

886
00:50:22,800 --> 00:50:26,040
<font color="#ffffff">Confronting her might backfire</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and drive her away.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

887
00:50:26,120 --> 00:50:27,440
<font color="#ffffff">How about this?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

888
00:50:27,520 --> 00:50:29,200
<font color="#ffffff">We can use the same plan as before.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

889
00:50:29,280 --> 00:50:31,520
<font color="#ffffff">NEXT EPISODE</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

890
00:50:31,600 --> 00:50:33,760
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you running away? What happened?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

891
00:50:33,840 --> 00:50:35,880
<font color="#ffffff">Petch, I don't want to stay here anymore.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

892
00:50:35,960 --> 00:50:37,240
<font color="#ffffff">Take me somewhere else.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

893
00:50:37,320 --> 00:50:39,960
<font color="#ffffff">They wanted you</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to have the perfect partner.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

894
00:50:40,040 --> 00:50:41,800
<font color="#ffffff">But I don't love him.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

895
00:50:42,760 --> 00:50:44,480
<font color="#ffffff">You still don't know</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

896
00:50:45,480 --> 00:50:46,640
<font color="#ffffff">where my heart is.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

897
00:51:02,080 --> 00:51:07,280
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I wish I knew if I ever crossed your mind</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

898
00:51:08,200 --> 00:51:13,320
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I wish I knew if you heard the whisper</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

899
00:51:14,160 --> 00:51:20,120
<font color="#ffffff"><i>For my heart is crying out my love</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>It's deep and true</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

900
00:51:20,200 --> 00:51:24,960
<font color="#ffffff"><i>But never reaching you</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

901
00:51:26,200 --> 00:51:31,280
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I know that it simply cannot be</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

902
00:51:32,240 --> 00:51:37,240
<font color="#ffffff"><i>And I never want to cause you misery</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

903
00:51:38,600 --> 00:51:43,920
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I'm just an ordinary man</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Worth nothing at all</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

904
00:51:44,720 --> 00:51:49,480
<font color="#ffffff"><i>And I never want to make</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Your teardrops fall</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

905
00:51:51,560 --> 00:51:55,520
<font color="#ffffff"><i>You are out of reach</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

906
00:51:56,120 --> 00:52:01,320
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Is it a crime that I need you?</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

907
00:52:03,320 --> 00:52:08,000
<font color="#ffffff"><i>Please let me know for sure</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

908
00:52:08,080 --> 00:52:13,360
<font color="#ffffff"><i>That you're the one I've been waiting for</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

909
00:52:14,240 --> 00:52:18,960
<font color="#ffffff"><i>How much longer can I bear this pain?</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

910
00:52:20,280 --> 00:52:25,240
<font color="#ffffff"><i>How much longer must I wait in vain?</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

911
00:52:26,200 --> 00:52:31,160
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I really don't know what move to make</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

912
00:52:32,200 --> 00:52:37,840
<font color="#ffffff"><i>To end this heartache</i></font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff"><i>And say that I love you</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font></font>

913
00:52:37,920 --> 00:52:39,640
<font color="#ffffff">Subtitle translation by: Jarut K.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>
